should have to bear.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/115800/extras/9e9d1cd55f5cbaba392e8c9f2be9ad8e.webp?t=1770948904\" width=270 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/115800/extras/7cf00178204cc193a73331501a4ab764.apng?t=1770948904\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/115800/extras/7cf00178204cc193a73331501a4ab764.poster.avif?t=1770948904\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A love letter to pixel art for a new audience, Owlboy is a story-driven action adventure, with a unique mix of flight and platforming.<br></li><li>Carry anything. Recruit Otus’s friends as gunners to fight for you, each with unique abilities and stories.<br></li><li>Large dungeons with big and challenging boss battles.<br></li><li>An adventure 10 years in the making.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/115800/extras/0b6d6fe3211e10b76aec7765376401c9.poster.avif?t=1770948904\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/115800/extras/0b6d6fe3211e10b76aec7765376401c9.webm?t=1770948904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/115800/extras/0b6d6fe3211e10b76aec7765376401c9.mp4?t=1770948904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Want to connect with Owlboy fans, and get instant tips/tricks for the game! Join our Discord today (link in side panel)!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/115800/extras/225580f7445b3bb5c5615bab942d77ce.avif?t=1770948904\" width=60