      "review_text": "Owlboy is a sweet game clearly made by a group of people who put their whole hearts into it. The art and music alone are worth the price, too. The story is sweet and the gameplay is pretty straightforward, so it's easy to pick up. Plus you can beat it in a few sittings.",
